{"comments":"Pure formatting functions for display\n\nThis module provides pure, easily testable functions for formatting:\n- Bytes (KB, MB, GB, TB)\n- Numbers (compact notation, percentages)\n- Durations (seconds, minutes, hours)\n- Common calculations (percentages, rates)\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Format bytes as human-readable string with space separator\n\n```purescript\nformatBytes 1024.0 == \"1.0 KB\"\nformatBytes (2.5 * gb) == \"2.5 GB\"\nformatBytes 0.0 == \"0 B\"\nformatBytes (-1024.0) == \"-1.0 KB\"\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[68,32],"name":".spago/p/hydrogen/d7075f327b505a6b238b541c9857f90441739364/src/Hydrogen/Data/Format.purs","start":[68,1]},"title":"formatBytes"},{"children":[],"comments":"Compact byte format without space separator\n\n```purescript\nformatBytesCompact (1.5 * gb) == \"1.5GB\"\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[83,39],"name":".spago/p/hydrogen/d7075f327b505a6b238b541c9857f90441739364/src/Hydrogen/Data/Format.purs","start":[83,1]},"title":"formatBytesCompact"},{"children":[],"comments":"Parse a bytes string back to number\nReturns Nothing for invalid input\n\n```purescript\nparseBytes \"1.0 KB\" == Just 1024.0\nparseBytes \"invalid\" == Nothing\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents